# FEWD CA-3 FOOD WEBSITE
# Pure Plate Pleasure
# Overview
Pure Plate Pleasure is a delightful food website that aims to bring joy to your plate. Whether you're a seasoned chef or a cooking novice, our platform offers a variety of recipes, cooking tips, and food-related content to satisfy your culinary cravings. From appetizers to desserts, we strive to inspire and guide you on a journey of pure pleasure in the kitchen.

Features
1. Recipe Collection
2. Diverse Cuisines
3. Cooking Tips and Techniques
4. Seasonal Specials
5. Community and Interaction


The food items in the website are been accessed with the help of the API provided.
The website contains a a header which provides the decription of the website , below there is search where the user can search food based on the food categories (Examples - breakfast, vegan, dessert, chicken, etc.) By entering the categories the all the food items will get dislayed at the end of the website page.
Below the header the section for diaplaying the random images after reloading the page, the user the can see the particular food ingredients.


# Techical details:
The website is create using HTML, CSS and javascript.
Various food items in the wwebsite are accessed with the following API https://www.themealdb.com/api.php
The website is  made responsive for usage on various devices.
 